➜脆皮雪糕在家就能做，是真的吗？
http://www.sohu.com/a/411020455_114960	3960
<p><strong>(央视财经《是真的吗》)</strong>炎炎夏日，酷暑难耐，<span>怎么在家自制</span><span>脆皮雪糕</span><span>呢？</span></p>
<p><span>首先，准备</span><span>好</span><span>200克酸奶</span><span>、</span><span>200克淡奶油</span><span>、</span><span>200克黑巧克力</span><span>和</span><span>40克椰子油</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200802/6988e3e250b74d558a85c5aa0b052e72.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>把淡奶油打发好。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200802/9cbcca17b9ea44a4935cbfca6d30e5e1.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>酸奶和淡奶油按</span><span><strong>1:1的比例</strong></span><span>搅拌均匀。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200802/b30098a853d8496b8742fdbb7a9b9b9d.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
